title: I didn't recieve my little devil teemo icon
body: I have beaten the doom bots a long time ago and i still didn't receive the icon.

replies.body:
As *Zombiemaster* mentioned, we're still granting these icons in waves until **November 17th**. If you don't have it by then, please reach out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).

Let me know if you have any questions.
The icons can take up to 2 weeks after the end of the Teemoing event to be added to your account, so you can expect to receive them by November 17th at the latest.
